@douglass_freedmen_mobilization
title: Mobilize the Freedmen
subtitle: Douglass travels through the South organizing freedmen communities and Union Leagues.
choose-if: advisor_action_timer = 0
unavailable-subtitle: [? if advisor_action_timer > 0 : [+ advisor_action_timer +] months before next advisor action. ?]
