@douglass_international_reputation
title: Leverage International Reputation
subtitle: Douglass's international fame is used to build support for Reconstruction abroad.
choose-if: advisor_action_timer = 0
unavailable-subtitle: [? if advisor_action_timer > 0 : [+ advisor_action_timer +] months before next advisor action. ?]
on-arrival: advisor_action_timer = 6; last_advisor_action = 1; europe_relation += 4;

Douglass corresponds with European abolitionists, reform movements, and liberal politicians, framing American Reconstruction as part of a global struggle for human freedom. European liberal opinion, already sympathetic, shifts further in our favor — making it harder for foreign governments to treat the former Confederacy as a legitimate grievance.